{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126790/extras/wordo_normal.png?t=1736012974\" />Hi there!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wordban</strong> is a text-based Sokoban-style game. Guide the adorable <strong>Wordo</strong> to push boxes and trigger each level's innovative text rules, altering the boxes' layout, quantity, and even attributes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With your strategy, <strong>Wordo</strong> can make boxes multiply, merge into one, drip through stone, and even turn into gold!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126790/extras/description_gameplay.gif?t=1736012974\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 100 meticulously designed levels are the long life paths you will accompany\u00a0<strong>Wordo\u00a0</strong>through.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126790/extras/description_chapter1.gif?t=1736012974\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126790/extras/wordo_ei.png?t=1736012974\" />Can you overcome the tricky traps or resonate with some humorous twists? Whether you're pondering deeply or experiencing sudden enlightenment, these are the delightful moments <strong>Wordban</strong> wants to share with you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126790/extras/wordo_uwu.png?t=1736012974\" />Awaken <strong>Wordo</strong> and enjoy the special puzzle-solving fun!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126790/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736012974","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126790/page.bg.jpg?t=1736012974","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126790/397f0c8a103c76a1d94b36fa357a2c242044303f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736012974","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126790/397f0c8a103c76a1d94b36fa357a2c242044303f/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736012974","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":30},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3202180,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126790/extras/wordo_normal.png?t=1736012974\" />Hi there!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wordban</strong> is a text-based Sokoban-style game. Guide the adorable <strong>Wordo</strong> to push boxes and trigger each level's innovative text rules, altering the boxes' layout, quantity, and even attributes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With your strategy, <strong>Wordo</strong> can make boxes multiply, merge into one, drip through stone, and even turn into gold!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/